## Drivers

- `vault_fs` enabled · `search` ships disabled (`tools/search_server.py`, Serper/Tavily)
- Closed by default: skill YAML `tools:` allowlist
- Exec-tagged → IVT `TOOL_EXEC_APPROVAL`; Tier 1 approve: `POST /api/v1/skills/interrupts/{id}/approve`

## API quick reference

- `GET /api/v1/runs/stats?window_days=7` — dogfooding go/no-go
