- `GET /api/v1/skills/recovery` · `POST /api/v1/skills/recovery/resolve`
- `GET /api/v1/health`

## Gemini

- Default `gemini-2.5-flash-lite`; per-model budget ledger counts every API attempt
- Degraded auto-clears after retry window; vault text UTF-8/UTF-16 tolerant in RAG

